    "We express it as \"[ ssrc | c | r = stgt ]\" when a text span ssrc with a particular component label c depends on another text span stgt via a relation label r. However, we omit stgt and the relation label r if the span ssrc is independent of others, indicating it as \"[ ssrc | c ]\".",
